<!-- ##### SECTION Short_Description ##### -->

Initializing the library

<!-- ##### SECTION Long_Description ##### -->
<para>

Before any operation are done using the requiem library, the user first need 
to initialize it using the requiem_init() function.

<programlisting>
int ret;

ret = requiem_init(&amp;argc, argv);
if ( ret &lt; 0 ) {
        requiem_perror(ret, "unable to initialize the requiem library");
        return -1;
}
</programlisting>

</para>

